# Contributing to the Phoenix Constitution

We welcome principled, respectful contributions from all backgrounds. You may contribute by:

- Submitting issues with suggestions, critiques, or additions
- Forking the repository and opening pull requests with article revisions
- Emailing anonymous proposals to phoenixconstitution@proton.me

When proposing edits:
- Reference specific sections or articles
- Include rationale for change
- Maintain inclusive, rights-based, and democratic alignment

All contributions will be evaluated based on structural integrity, enforceability, and moral clarity.

Thank you for carrying the fire.
